 ---\")\n","\n","# 1. Count negatives and zeros for each mineral individually\n","for col in mineral_targets:\n","    neg_count = (gdf_occ[col] < 0).sum()\n","    zero_count = (gdf_occ[col] == 0).sum()\n","    print(f\"{col}: {neg_count:,} negative values (BDL) | {zero_count:,} zero values (Missing)\")\n","\n","# 2. Identify and count 'Ghost Rows' (rows where all 5 minerals are exactly 0)\n","ghost_mask = (gdf_occ[mineral_targets] == 0).all(axis=1)\n","ghost_rows_count = ghost_mask.sum()\n","\n","print(f\"\\n--- Ghost Row Analysis ---\")\n","print(f\"Number of rows with 0 across ALL 5 minerals: {ghost_rows_count:,}\")\n","print(f\"Total dataset size: {len(gdf_occ):,}\")"],"execution_count":14,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["--- Mineral Target Semantic Investigation ---\n","AU: 98,398 negative values (BDL) | 349,335 zero values (Missing)\n","AG: 152,470 negative values (BDL) | 310,504 zero values (Missing)\n","CU: 45,498 negative values (BDL) | 210,425 zero values (Missing)\n","CO: 25,055 negative values (BDL) | 326,450 zero values (Missing)\n","NI: 52,762 negative values (BDL) | 294,971 zero values (Missing)\n","\n","--- Ghost Row Analysis ---\n","Number of rows with 0 across ALL 5 minerals: 185,308\n","Total dataset size: 582,192\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### Ground Truth Refinement: Below Detection vs. Missing Data\n","Following our investigation, we establish the following data semantics:\n","1. **Negative Values (e.g., -1, -5)**: Ground-truthed as 'Below Detection Limit' (BDL). We will convert these to **0** to represent a valid low-concentration measurement.\n","2. **Zero Values (0)**: Identified as 'Not Assayed' (missing data). We will replace the 0 values and replace them with NaN for now\n","3. **0 rows** Further, minerals without any data across all 5 are useless, so we will remove those\n"],"metadata":{"id":"iceKYSczdXao"}},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":458